cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.SE 

The paper discusses the issue of security threats in IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed approach uses neural networks (cs.AI) and binary visualisation (cs.LG) to detect and classify new malware. The paper also involves network analysis (cs.NI) and software engineering (cs.SE) in the implementation of the proposed approach.
